Description: monitor and alert on runaway Koha Starman workers
 A small daemon that periodically scans /proc for Koha Starman worker
 processes and posts a Slack alert when a worker exceeds configured
 runtime or memory thresholds. On alert, it captures a streaming-gzipped
 strace of the offending process and includes the tail in the Slack
 message. Designed to be installed on Koha hosts and managed by systemd.
